<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
Dear <%= @new_user.name %>,
<p>
  A login to the <%= APPLICATION_NAME %> website has been set up for you by <%= mail_to @added_by.email, @added_by.name %>.
  Here is your new login information:
</p>

<div><strong>Web address:</strong> <%= link_to @url, @url %></div>
<div><strong>Username:</strong> <%= @new_user.email %></div>

You can log in and reset your password by going to <%= link_to @url, @url %> in the next <% @hours_to_log_in %> hours.

If you don't log in in the next <% @hours_to_log_in %> hours, no worries. You can reset your password by going to <%= link_to 'Account | Reset Password', profile_edit_password_url %> </p>

</body>
</html>